317
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:57,269
Tolong putar bahu anda perlahan.

318
00:27:00,309 --> 00:27:01,440
Rasanya jauh lebih baik.

319
00:27:02,339 --> 00:27:03,410
Syukurlah.

320
00:27:06,910 --> 00:27:10,519
Ta-da. Let's see!

321
00:27:10,849 --> 00:27:11,920
Ini kantorku.

322
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:17,630
Jadi itulah kenapa kau kembali.

323
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:20,690
Pergi ke klinik luar negeri sangat buruk.

324
00:27:21,029 --> 00:27:23,900
Aku mendapat perawatan bahu di Australia.

325
00:27:24,170 --> 00:27:25,630
Tapi aku ingin rehabilitasi di Korea.

326
00:27:25,630 --> 00:27:28,569
Kau pasti sudah jatuh saat berselancar.

327
00:27:28,569 --> 00:27:31,009
Ombaknya sangat bagus.

328
00:27:31,009 --> 00:27:32,440
Orang bilang aku tidak boleh masuk, tapi...

329
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:34,309
