330
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,180
Dan ada batu disana.

331
00:27:37,009 --> 00:27:39,609
Bagaimanapun, apa dia profesional?

332
00:27:39,609 --> 00:27:40,980
Dia pria yang diinginkan semua orang.

333
00:27:40,980 --> 00:27:42,250
Aku harus ngomong apa lagi?

334
00:27:42,519 --> 00:27:44,890
Kau bisa langsung tau saat melihatnya.

335
00:27:46,019 --> 00:27:47,690
Jangan main mata dengannya.

336
00:27:47,690 --> 00:27:48,819
Jangan sampai berani.

337
00:27:49,319 --> 00:27:51,190
Ada seorang pria yang kuinginkan.

338
00:27:51,490 --> 00:27:53,559
